The first episode of The Grand Tour was illegally downloaded more than 7.9 million times, Daily Mail reported. “It has overtaken every big show, including Game Of Thrones, for the totals across different platforms,” said MUSO. The Grand Tour is now the most illegally-downloaded show in history, according to the report. According to MUSO’s findings, viewers in Britain were the worst culprits – making up 13.7% of the total number of downloads. Episode two of The Grand Tour saw 6.4 million downloads, and the third episode was downloaded 4.6 million times. Amazon said the first episode of The Grand Tour was the biggest show premiere ever on Amazon Prime Video.